import akka.actor.Actor
import java.util.Date

object Tpch22 {
  import Helper._
  val precision = 7; // significative numbers (7 to pass r_sumdivgrp, 10 otherwise)
  val diff_p = Math.pow(0.1,precision)
  
  def execute(args:Array[String],f:List[Any]=>Unit) = bench(args,(d:String,p:Int,t:Long)=>run[Tpch22](Seq(
    (new java.io.FileInputStream("/Users/dashti/Documents/MyWorkspaces/DATASRC/dbtoaster/experiments/data/tpch/"+d+"/orders.csv"),new Adaptor.CSV("ORDERS","long,long,string,double,date,string,string,long,string","\\Q|\\E",if(d.endsWith("_del")) "ins+del" else "insert"),Split()),
    (new java.io.FileInputStream("/Users/dashti/Documents/MyWorkspaces/DATASRC/dbtoaster/experiments/data/tpch/"+d+"/customer.csv"),new Adaptor.CSV("CUSTOMER","long,string,string,long,string,double,string,string","\\Q|\\E",if(d.endsWith("_del")) "ins+del" else "insert"),Split())
  ),p,t),f)
  
  def main(args:Array[String]) {
    execute(args,(res:List[Any])=>{
      println("NUMCUST:\n"+M3Map.toStr(res(0))+"\n")
      println("TOTALACCTBAL:\n"+M3Map.toStr(res(1))+"\n")
    })
  }
